history.content:
Hi all, 

We have a new tag/folder, "peer_directed". Please use this for questions directed to fellow students. For example: 

  • Has anyone taken STAT 134 over the summer (8 week session C)? How is it compared to STAT 134 during the year?
  • What's a relatively low work breadth class that's still open?
  •  EE105 v CS170. Which is bigger workload?

We ask that students please help answer their peer's questions when possible.

  • Topics staff can address: Department policy, major & minor requirements, enrollment updates, enrichment opportunities, declaration procedure, tutoring & academic.
  • Topics staff may not address: CalCentral issues, feedback on course combinations, college/financial aid policy, specifics of certain courses, tech support, other majors/departments, etc
